      "patchset_number": 13,
      "line": 28,
      "message": "As per my understanding and working with SOL003 adapter in SO module, i believe you are using wrong API for getting vnfms from AAI ESR, there are two APIs \n\n- ESR GUI API  https://docs.onap.org/en/latest/submodules/aai/esr-gui.git/docs/index.html\n- ESR Server API https://docs.onap.org/en/latest/submodules/aai/esr-server.git/docs/index.html\n\nI think you should be using the server API? (https://docs.onap.org/en/latest/submodules/aai/esr-server.git/docs/platform/consumedapis.html). \n\nWith the SOL003 Adapter our team implemented the ESR server API see AaiServiceProviderImpl class for example",
      "author": {
